[
  {
    "id": "7719025806939589148",
    "author_id": "3747882729217115656",
    "text": "My latest letter is up in the Capital Gazette this morning, on why the county's stormwater fee is worth keeping. Runoff into the Severn doesn't fix itself. capgaznews.com/opinion",
    "created_at": "2026-10-28T00:16:47+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "7108442956301887744",
    "like_count": "30",
    "retweet_count": "5",
    "reply_count": "8",
    "quote_count": "2"
  },
  {
    "id": "4467334678503439837",
    "author_id": "3747882729217115656",
    "text": "Reread the 1964 Wilderness Act debates this week. Striking how much of the language was hammered out line by line over eight years. We forget durable policy is slow work.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-28T11:12:55+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "6620183048871209472",
    "like_count": "43",
    "retweet_count": "2",
    "reply_count": "2",
    "quote_count": "0"
  },
  {
    "id": "5710416000425606921",
    "author_id": "3747882729217115656",
    "text": "First prothonotary warbler of the season along the Severn seawall this morning. Small flash of gold in the low branches. Worth the early walk.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-28T18:21:54+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "5417820033118732288",
    "like_count": "39",
    "retweet_count": "5",
    "reply_count": "6",
    "quote_count": "1"
  },
  {
    "id": "3666503891724697464",
    "author_id": "3747882729217115656",
    "text": "Thirty-five years at Interior taught me that a land-management rule is only as good as the monitoring behind it. A rule you can't measure is a press release.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-28T23:23:12+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "5199048820117610496",
    "like_count": "10",
    "retweet_count": "4",
    "reply_count": "6",
    "quote_count": "0"
  },
  {
    "id": "8791745244536100650",
    "author_id": "3747882729217115656",
    "text": "New letter in this weekend's Capital Gazette: the case for the county library keeping its Sunday hours. A branch open is a public good you can walk to.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-28T15:56:17+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "8033719205488001024",
    "like_count": "14",
    "retweet_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "3",
    "quote_count": "2"
  },
  {
    "id": "9993769660145514872",
    "author_id": "3747882729217115656",
    "text": "Watercolor of a great blue heron I've been working on all week. Beginner's hands, but the light on the water finally came through. Practice is its own reward.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-28T14:32:55+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "9271108440255938560",
    "like_count": "53",
    "retweet_count": "1",
    "reply_count": "8",
    "quote_count": "0"
  },
  {
    "id": "4829900097971756121",
    "author_id": "3747882729217115656",
    "text": "Teaching a free online unit on the history of climate policy this summer. If you think the 1970 Clean Air Act arrived fully formed, the committee record will surprise you.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-28T04:18:28+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "4460925310028922880",
    "like_count": "59",
    "retweet_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "2",
    "quote_count": "0"
  },
  {
    "id": "5507718779216456227",
    "author_id": "3747882729217115656",
    "text": "Oyster restoration numbers on the Bay are quietly one of the better environmental stories of the decade. Slow, unglamorous, and it is actually working.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-28T14:26:29+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "5083344011927191552",
